HTML Fundamentals

Overview

HTML drives the weh, Whether you use E. Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or some other browser, many of us use the web daily. In this course you will learn the fundamental elements of creating web pages using HTML

Not covered in this course is detailed information about CSS. javascript, or HIIP as those topics are covered in detail in other Abdullah courses 12

Objectives

Explain the fundamental concepts of HTML Have fun cresting documents

creating memories

Mark it up!

